    </div>

    <div style="height: 200px; width: 100px; border: 3px dashed #e03c32; float: left">
        <p>
            <strong><a href="/">Years list</a></strong> <br/>
            <strong><a href="/year2019">Month list</a></strong><br/>
            <strong><a href="/statistics">Statistics</a></strong>

